OL,3,COsian Roberts rules himself out of
OL,4,Crace to be new Wales manager
OL,6,FOsian Roberts has ruled himself out of
OL,7,Fthe race to be the next Wales football
OL,8,Fmanager.
OL,10,FThe former Wales assistant coach - who
OL,11,Fserved as an assistant to former Wales
OL,12,Fbosses Gary Speed, Chris Coleman and
OL,13,FRyan Giggs - has confirmed he will not
OL,14,Fbe succeeding Rob Page, who was sacked
OL,15,Fin June following disappointing
OL,16,Ffriendlies against Gibraltar and
OL,17,FSlovakia.
OL,19,FThe Football Association of Wales is
OL,20,Fin the early stages of its search for
OL,21,Fa new manager.
