OL,3,COsian Roberts rules himself out of
OL,4,Crace to be new Wales manager
OL,6,FRoberts, who left the FAW in 2019 to
OL,7,Fspend two years as Crystal Palace
OL,8,Fassistant manager, guided second-tier
OL,9,FItalian outfit Como into Serie A last
OL,10,Fseason and has committed his future to
OL,11,Fthe club, adding that he was grateful
OL,12,Fto be approached by the FAW about the
OL,13,Fposition.
OL,15,FPosting on social media, Roberts said:
OL,16,F"I would like to thank the Football
OL,17,FAssociation of Wales for expressing an
OL,18,Finterest in approaching me regarding
OL,19,Fthe role of Wales national team
OL,20,Fmanager.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
