OL,3,COsian Roberts rules himself out of
OL,4,Crace to be new Wales manager
OL,6,F"As an incredibly passionate and proud
OL,7,FWelshman I would love to become
OL,8,Fmanager of Wales one day.
OL,10,F"Currently, however, I am on an
OL,11,Fincredible journey with Como 1907
OL,12,Fhaving helped lead them to an
OL,13,Fhistorical promotion to Serie A.
OL,15,F"I am committed to this wonderful club
OL,16,Fand our exciting project until at
OL,17,Fleast 2026 and am forever thankful for
OL,18,Ftheir support and faith in me.
